@notice Approximation of the Probability Density Function.
@dev Equal to `Z(x) = (1 / 2)e^( (-(x - )^2) / 2^2 )`.
Only computes pdf of a distribution with  = 0 and  = 1.
@custom:rounding Rounds down via truncation from division.
